   OWENS-CORNING FIBERGLAS (Toledo) -- Max O. Weber, 60 years
old, was named chief executive officer of this manufacturer
of glass-fiber products, succeeding William W. Boeschenstein.
Mr. Boeschenstein, 64, will retire in September. He will
remain a director. Mr. Weber, who joined Owens-Corning in
